INSERT INTO `hy_blog` VALUES ('30', '再也回不去的 GitHub....', '<p style=\"outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, \" sf=\"\" ui=\"\" text\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" \"pingfang=\"\" sc\",=\"\" \"hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" \"wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" hei\",=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" simhei,=\"\" simsun;\"=\"\"><b>相信大家都知道了，据 Bloomberg 报道，微软确认要收购 GitHub 了，虽然官方还没宣布，但是这事基本八九不离十了。具体多少钱收购的还不得而知，但是据知情人士透漏，GitHub 之所以放弃了原有的上市计划，而选择出售给微软，部分原因是因为他们对微软 CEO 萨提亚·纳德拉印象非常深刻。</b></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, \" sf=\"\" ui=\"\" text\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" \"pingfang=\"\" sc\",=\"\" \"hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" \"wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" hei\",=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" simhei,=\"\" simsun;\"=\"\"><u>嗯，这大概就是所谓的「确认过眼神」吧。</u></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, \" sf=\"\" ui=\"\" text\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" \"pingfang=\"\" sc\",=\"\" \"hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" \"wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" hei\",=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" simhei,=\"\" simsun;\"=\"\">GitHub 被微软收购，网上一大堆程序员嘲讽，很多人可能会觉得微软的产品挺好的，纳闷为什么被嘲讽？</p><p style=\"outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, \" sf=\"\" ui=\"\" text\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" \"pingfang=\"\" sc\",=\"\" \"hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" \"wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" hei\",=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" simhei,=\"\" simsun;\"=\"\"><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" data-filename=\"adaf2edda3cc7cd9019ce04e3501213fb90e91f0.jpg\" style=\"width: 450px;\"><br></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, \" sf=\"\" ui=\"\" text\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" \"pingfang=\"\" sc\",=\"\" \"hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" \"wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" hei\",=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" simhei,=\"\" simsun;\"=\"\"><br></p><p style=\"outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, \" sf=\"\" ui=\"\" text\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" \"pingfang=\"\" sc\",=\"\" \"hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" \"wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" hei\",=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" simhei,=\"\" simsun;\"=\"\">其实，在硅谷，嘲讽微软非常普遍，硅谷的码农门喜欢 Google、Facebook 这类开放、年轻的公司，而微软一直给人的感觉是封闭、守旧，自然不被硅谷的码农们待见。</p><p style=\"outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, \" sf=\"\" ui=\"\" text\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" \"pingfang=\"\" sc\",=\"\" \"hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" \"wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" hei\",=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" simhei,=\"\" simsun;\"=\"\">其实最近的 10 年，开源非常流行，GitHub 也是在这期间发展起来的，逐渐的成为程序员最喜欢的开源社区，众多科技顶尖公司也纷纷加入开源的怀抱，这几年微软看到形势后，说实话，也没以前那么封闭了，为开源界也做出了不少贡献。还记得 2017 年 GitHub 年度报告么？其中一项为开源社区贡献最多的组织竟然是微软。</p><p style=\"outline: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-bottom: 16px; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); line-height: 26px; text-align: justify; word-break: break-all; font-family: -apple-system, \" sf=\"\" ui=\"\" text\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" \"pingfang=\"\" sc\",=\"\" \"hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" gb\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" yahei\",=\"\" \"wenquanyi=\"\" micro=\"\" hei\",=\"\" sans-serif,=\"\" simhei,=\"\" simsun;\"=\"\">然而当时那项结果其实不准确，因为那是统计了历年来的所有的记录，Medium 上有一位程序员重新统计了过去一年的记录，相对来说更有说服力：</p>', '1528249482', '0', '1528109670', null, '3', '1');
